ids.bio:
Hello, my name is Teun, and I live in Amsterdam.

I am trying to make something of my life in extremely convoluted ways. My proudest achievement so far is my Patreon url.

I focus on writing fiction, making original music, visual art and the occasional essay. If you support me, I will like you forever, and I will "owe you one".
